          div.top
            h1 Mentor Application
            form.form-horizontal#signupFormtor(method="post" action="/auth/signup")
               input.span3(type="hidden" name="role" value="mentor")
               label Username
               input.span3(id="username", type="text", name="user", placeholder="Create User Name")
               label Password
               input.span3(id="password", type="password", name="password", placeholder="Create Password")
               label Email
               input.span3(id="email" type="email" name="email" placeholder="enter email")
            
               h3 Introduce yourself!
               p Tell us about you. Write a little summary to help potential mentors or mentees get to know you?
                        textarea(class="form-control" id="summary" name="summary" rows="4" placeholder="Type answer here")


               h3 Languages
               p Please click on the language that you are interested in using during mentorship
                  
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios1(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='C Language')
                     | C language
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios2(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='C++')
                     | C++
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios3(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='C#')
                     | C#
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios4(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='Objective C')
                     | Objective C
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios5(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='Java')
                     | Java
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios6(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='PHP')
                     | PHP
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios7(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='Python')
                     | Python
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios8(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='Ruby')
                     | Ruby
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios9(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='JavaScript')
                     | JavaScript
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios10(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='node')
                     | node.js
               .radio
                  label
                     input#optionsRadios11(type='radio' name='optionsRadios' value='other')
                     | other
                        
               h3 What area are you from?
                .checkbox-inline
                  label
                      input#inlineCheckbox1(type='checkbox' name='optionsinCheck' value='Denver')
                      | Denver
                .checkbox-inline
                  label
                      input#inlineCheckbox2(type='checkbox' name='optionsinCheck' value='Boulder')
                      | Boulder
               h3 What level of coder do you consider yourself?
                .checkbox
                  label
                      input#checkbox(type='checkbox' name='optionsCheck' value='Beginning Beginner')
                      | Beginning Beginner
                .checkbox
                  label
                      input#checkbox(type='checkbox' name='optionsCheck' value='Solid Begninner')
                      | Advanced Beginner
                .checkbox
                  label
                      input#checkbox(type='checkbox' name='optionsCheck' value='Intermediate')
                      | Intermediate
                .checkbox
                  label
                      input#checkbox(type='checkbox' name='optionsCheck' value='Advanced')
                      | Advanced





               h3 Why Mentor?

               p When entering into a mentoring partnership, both parties commit to a shared effort. Mentoring is a great gift.  Please take some time to help us better understand why you want to mentor and your goals in being a mentor.


                     p What are your goals in working with a mentee?
                        textarea(class="form-control" id="goalsMentor" name="goals" rows="4" placeholder="Type answer here")
                     
                     p How do you plan to mentor budding women coders?  (Think about your personality, tempermanet and teaching style.)
                        textarea(class="form-control" id="teachingStyle" name="teaching" rows="4" placeholder="Type answer here")

                     p What is your availability?
                        textarea(class="form-control" id="availability" name="avail" rows="4" placeholder="Type answer here")

                     p What are some of your interests and hobbies?
                        textarea(class="form-control" id="interestsMentor" name="hobbies" rows="4" placeholder="Type answer here")

                     input.btn(type="submit", value="submit")















